"         Patient information: Ischemic stroke treatment (Beyond the Basics)",
"        </a>",
"       </dd>",
"       <dd>",
"        <a href=\"UTD.htm?37/37/38484\">",
"         Patient information: Stroke symptoms and diagnosis (Beyond the Basics)",
"        </a>",
"       </dd>",
"      </dl>",
"      <div id=\"tooltipper\">",
"      </div>",
